data.description: Enjoy the beautiful Calaveras sunsets and foothill views from the front balcony of this hilltop home! This 3 bedroom 2 bath home sits on over a half-acre and features several custom touches including arched doorways, tray ceilings, window alcove, and a vaulted wood beamed ceiling. The pellet stove and red brick hearth create a cozy focal point in the living room and will keep you toasty warm during the winters. A spacious primary bedroom and bathroom include a walk in closet and dual vanity, the laundry room is on the main floor and is complete with storage cabinets. The private back patio is covered and makes a perfect spot for entertaining guests. This rolling hillside parcel is spotted with beautiful oaks ready for your creative touch! Brand new HVAC system recently installed.
